<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 Oct 2021 10:22:26 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>【評測】Sony WF-C500 入門真無線耳機，音色表現優秀 + 平玩 Sony 耳機</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/HSoaauavN5U/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 22 Oct 2021 10:19:22 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[音樂耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[SONY]]></category><category><![CDATA[無線耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[真無線藍牙耳機]]></category><category><![CDATA[藍牙耳機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1066907</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Sony 真無線耳機 WM-1000XM4 在音質、解噪各方面都取得很不錯的水準與平衡，之不過未必每位手機用家 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Sony 真無線耳機 WM-1000XM4 在音質、解噪各方面都取得很不錯的水準與平衡，之不過未必每位手機用家都需要用到這麼強的耳機，如果想平玩 Sony 真無線耳機，現在就有 WF-C500。它繼承了 Sony 真無線耳機的精髓，包括音質、操作、DSEE、體積細小的機身等，但價錢只為旗艦機一半不到。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067241" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-2-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-2-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-2-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0017-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067242" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-2-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-2-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-2-768x421.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0019-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>WF-C500 可說是現在 Sony 入門級真無線耳機，雖然沒有降噪功能，也沒有 DSEE Extreme，但其他基本元素都跟旗艦跟到頗為十足，例如音色傾向，你聽開 Sony 耳機的話，重低音的份量、高頻／人聲的清晰度等等，不會讓你覺得 WF-C500 有太多不足，連接體驗、DSEE 音質提升技術還在，操作都是得心應手。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0018.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066945" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0018-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0018-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0018-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0018.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>外型輕巧，強勁續航力</h2><p>首先我們看看它的機身設計，同 XM4 比較可說再細一個碼，同之前的 WF-XB700 大致相同。機身細的好處是耳機塞進耳後，不會有一大塊東西突出來，在街上使用也不會太過養眼，保持你的型人姿態。我們耳仔較細的記者沙律戴上耳機，耳機只從耳廓突出少少，機身基本上能收入在耳廓當中。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067246" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066938" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066939" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>耳機雖然配上塑膠耳塞，但貼服性在小編的情況來說就剛剛好。而且耳機形狀不會太奇特，好容易找到佩戴耳機的方向，一塞入耳就可使用了。這方面其實 Sony 的入門級耳機一直都做得很不錯。</p><p>當然用料上會較 XM4 略為「入門」一點。但你不與旗艦 XM4 作比較的話，WF-C500 的觸感還是很不錯，特別是耳機操作按鍵用上實體鍵，比較不會容易按錯。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0014-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067244" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0014-1-694x454.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="454" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0014-1-694x454.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0014-1-768x502.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0014-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0016-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067243" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0016-2-694x432.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="432" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0016-2-694x432.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0016-2-768x478.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0016-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067245" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-1-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-1-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-1-768x506.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0011-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>耳機充電盒用上霧面塑膠設計，雖然單薄但重量只為 44g（耳機連充電盒），比起 XM4 的 54g，還有 Apple AirPods Pro 的 56g；WF-C500 單邊耳機的重量也只是 5g，比起 XM4 的 7g 再輕一點，帶它出街無疑可再減輕你的負擔。之不過耳機盒不支援無線充電，只能連接 USB Type-C 充電線。耳機本身的續航力為 10 小時，可說是非常長氣，在正常使用下小編也能體會此耳機的驚異續航力。不過充電盒的電力就只能為耳機增添多 10 小時續航力，不算太多，你可能需要較頻密為它充電。耳機設有快充功能，充電 10 分鐘可給你 1 小時額外播放時間。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066953" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0008-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066954" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0006-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0002-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066941" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Sony 耳機的基本優點也能在 WF-C500 中找到，例如單耳機傳輸模式、手機／電腦快速配對，你也可在 Headphones Connect 手機 App 當中設定耳機的控制、等化器、機身按鍵的操作方式等等。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-4-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066948" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-4-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-4-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-4-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-4-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-4-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-4-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0003-4-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲Sony 耳機一向有的耳朵形狀分析系統、等化器、360 Reality Audio 都支援<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-6-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-6-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-6-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-6-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-6-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-6-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-6-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0001-6-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲到選單最底可看到 DSEE 功能，它可為本身碼率不高的音樂，以數碼方式提升音質，但在高清音樂上就反而會令音色稍為下跌</p><h2>音質測試：音場中等、人聲與重低音表現優秀</h2><p>作為入門級耳機，WF-C500 仍使用了一個 5.8mm 的驅動單元，它令到高頻保持到一定清晰度之餘，重低音份量與厚度都相當不錯。在 iPhone 13 Pro Max 以 AAC 連接之下，小編甚至會覺得 WF-C500 的人聲與高頻會較 XM4 更為突出。</p><p>透過 MOOV 收聽泳兒《荊棘海》24bit 48kHz, 1663kbps FLAC 時，可體驗到人聲較為清脆，但不會太過尖刺的感覺，而且人聲會較近。音樂開始時的音場、包圍感與人聲迴響較集中，未有太過擴散。不過在進入歌曲核心部份，你會發現包圍感仍有一定水準，而且同時音樂背景的低頻部份，包括低音結他、低音大提琴低頻部份的演出厚重而有份量，歌曲暗黑感覺與人聲清晰度互相輝映。人聲部份不止獨唱部份，在音樂高潮演出時亦能有清晰表現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-5-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066951" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-5-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-5-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-5-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-5-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0000-5-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>收聽石山街《石山派》24bit 48kHz, 1873kbps FLAC 同樣發現到歌手的歌聲較好多耳機都突出，很少會被音樂遮蓋，但同樣歌聲會比較清脆尖銳一點。同剛才聽的《荊棘海》一樣音場也是點到即止。之不過歌曲中低頻部份的份量就很不錯，下潛度都能與其他高階耳機相比，歌曲中有好多獨特聲效都可以通過耳機感受得到。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066952" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unwire0007-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>總括來說，小編會覺得此耳機來聽流行曲可發揮它重低音、歌聲的平衡度。收聽抒情以至強勁的歌曲也能表現出眾，但會在純音樂表現方面沒有旗艦款好。WF-C500 也可說是較為「雜食性」的耳機，連接流動電話後，看 YouTube、Netflix 影片或者聽 ASMR 音效，其準確的中頻與強勁重低音都有助提升音效上的體驗。如果想音色再細膩一點、音場再廣一點，又要有齊 LDAC 等高頻寬藍牙連接方式的話，你才需要購買旗艦款式。</p><h2>總結：驅動單元交到貨，有齊 Sony 耳機基本體驗</h2><p>整體來說，WF-C500 在各方面的表現也屬於 Sony 上乘之作，耳機的驅動單元交到貨，加上其他 Sony 耳機一貫的操作體驗，HK$999 的建議零售價這樣來說也頗為抵玩，只是隔音要靠耳機本身耳塞的表現了。買來做運動或者對無線耳機沒有極端要求的朋友，也可留意這款 WF-C500。</p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=HSoaauavN5U:XSoE-ypULEw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=HSoaauavN5U:XSoE-ypULEw:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/HSoaauavN5U" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/22/sony-wf-c500-review/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sony-wf-c500-review</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>iPhone 12 成功擋子彈，南非餐廳老闆奇蹟保命</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/Kki8X_rRkcY/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[牙 Step]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 22 Oct 2021 08:35:35 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone]]></category><category><![CDATA[擋子彈]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1067321</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>一名 51 歲南非男子 Max Mqadi 在 10 月 14 日在自己的餐廳的停車場遇上兩名匪徒，並遭到槍擊 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>一名 51 歲南非男子 Max Mqadi 在 10 月 14 日在自己的餐廳的停車場遇上兩名匪徒，並遭到槍擊，身體多處受傷。在匪徒瞄準事主頭部射擊時，事主的 iPhone 為他擋了一槍，保住了性命。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067334" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unnamed-1-694x459.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unnamed-1-694x459.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/unnamed-1.jpeg 750w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>外媒 TimesLive 在 10 月 17 日報道，51 歲的南非男子 Max Mqadi 在 10 月 14 日夜晚離開自己的餐廳 Max’s Lifestyle Village 時，在停車場上車後有兩名匪徒走近。事主透露當時被兩名匪徒夾擊，連開 15 槍。事主的手腳多處受傷，其中一名匪徒向他頭部開槍，而這一發子彈擊中在事主的 iPhone 上。其後事主立即開車帶佛羅里達路報警，送到 Netcare Umhlanga 醫院治理，最後在 10 月 18 日出院。</p><p>Max Mqadi 事後將「中槍」的 iPhone 照片上傳到社交網站，他使用的是 iPhone 12 機型。見到 iPhone 機背的相機模組旁邊有一個子彈孔，而機身正面的螢幕就因為槍擊的衝擊力被震碎，圖片在社交網站中多次被分享。事件懷疑是政治報復，當局目前尚未拘捕疑犯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067332" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/5953293-1-694x473.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="473" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/5953293-1-694x473.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/5953293-1-768x524.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/5953293-1.jpeg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1067333" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/pHONE.jpeg" alt="" width="451" height="463" /></p><p class="p1">資料來源：<a href="https://www.timeslive.co.za/news/south-africa/2021-10-17-rags-to-riches-durban-businessman-max-mqadi-dodges-death/">TimesLive</a></p>
