</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/eQvz4usgrNs" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/22/tp-link-re500x-onemesh-wi-fi-extender/wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=tp-link-re500x-onemesh-wi-fi-extender</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>BTS 防彈少年團聯乘 HLDS   特別版外置 DVD 光碟機</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/v4N0P-nE0Rc/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 22 Oct 2021 04:53:49 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[影音產品]]></category><category><![CDATA[BTS 防彈少年團]]></category><category><![CDATA[光碟機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1067042</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>還記得第一次聽到「Dynamite」時候的那一份雀躍同感動，作為韓國 BTS 防彈少年團的第一首全英文歌，當然 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>還記得第一次聽到「Dynamite」時候的那一份雀躍同感動，作為韓國 BTS 防彈少年團的第一首全英文歌，當然非常之有紀念價值。為此 HLDS (Hitachi LG Data Storage) 破天荒聯乘 BTS 推出「BTS Dynamite 特別版外置 DVD 光碟機」，可讓用家透過 Windows 及 MacOS 電腦重溫 BTS 在舞台所帶來的感動。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-00purple-all-items.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-00purple-all-items-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-00purple-all-items-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-00purple-all-items-900x900.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-00purple-all-items-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-00purple-all-items-768x768.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-00purple-all-items.png 1392w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-01pink-items.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-01pink-items-580x580.png" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-01pink-items-580x580.png 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-01pink-items-900x900.png 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-01pink-items-120x120.png 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-01pink-items-768x768.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/01-m2-w-01en-01pink-items.png 1392w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display.png"><br /></a></p><p>「BTS DYNAMITE 特別版外置 DVD 光碟機」設有紫色及粉紅色兩個版本，兩款的外觀及包裝均以「Dynamite」的 MV 作為靈感而特別設計，整個外盒以及隨附的配件都印有「Dynamite」MV 埸景的相關物件，例如 MV 背景中多次出現的 Donut house 及 Disco house。外盒正面更特別印有 BTS 防彈少年團各成員的剪影，相信各位 fans 們絕對能逐個認出。此光碟機的機身極之纖薄，用家更可隨身攜帶，然後配合專用手機 App DISC LINK Platinum 及 TrueDVD+ 即可於手機上播放 CD 及 DVD 內容（註：流動平台只支援 Android 平板、Android 智慧型手機、Amazon Fire OS）。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/multios.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/multios-634x580.png" alt="" width="634" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/multios-634x580.png 634w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/multios-768x703.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/multios.png 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 634px" /></a></p><p>而光碟機的包裝外盒本身亦是一個展示盒，讓各位 BTS fans 可以隨意於桌上展出精美的「Dynamite」特別版 DVD 光碟機機身。除此之外，特別版 DVD 光碟機更內附 3 隻專為特別版機身而設的保護光碟。用家可隨自己喜好及心情更換所愛的插畫放置於擁有透明上蓋的 DVD 機身內展示。</p><p>最後「BTS DYNAMITE 特別版外置 DVD 光碟機」的兩個版本亦非常貼心地隨附限量的 BTS Dynamite 貼紙，讓用家於展示盒或自己心愛的物件貼上，絕對是各位 BTS 防彈少年團 fans 不可以錯過的週邊產品。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1067046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display-694x375.png" alt="" width="694" height="375" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display-694x375.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display-1280x693.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display-768x416.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display-1536x831.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display-2048x1108.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/display.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>HLDS x BTS DYNAMITE 特別版外置 DVD 光碟機產品介紹網站：<a href="https://www.hornington.com/promotion/HLDS/HLDS%20x%20BTS/">https://www.hornington.com/promotion/HLDS/HLDS%20x%20BTS/</a></p><p>HLDS x BTS DYNAMITE 特別版外置 DVD 光碟機宣傳片：</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_26047"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zU_IFDd1qjQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><h2>產品詳細規格</h2><p>本體尺寸：144mm x 14mm x 137mm</p><p>本體重量：210g</p><p>接口：USB 2.0 (480Mbps), Micro USB Type-B 插口 (DVD 讀寫器)</p><p>數據傳輸率：讀取 CD 最大 24x, DVD：最大 8x ; 寫入 CD 最大 24x, DVD：最大 8x</p><p>兼容系：Windows, Mac OS, Android, Fire OS</p><h2>內容物：</h2><p>1 x 舞台盒 Stage Box (包裝盒)</p><p>1 x Dynamite 多系統 DVD 讀寫器</p><p>1 x USB Micro-B to Type-A 傳輸線</p><p>1 x USB Micro-B to Type-C 傳輸線</p><p>3 x 保護光碟 Protection Plate</p><p>2 x BTS Dynamite 貼紙</p><p>1 x 頂針</p><p>1 x 說明書</p><p>查詢：漢科電腦公司 (3626 9899)</p></p><div class="feedflare">
